  • Constructor Details

    • Matiere

      public Matiere(String labelMatiere, int heure_TD, int heure_TP, int heure_CM, int heure_projet, float Poid_CC, String Type_CC, float Poid_CT, String Type_CT, float poidMatiere)
      Permit to create an object Matier that will store all the infos about a subject.
      Parameters:
      labelMatiere - the name of the subject
      heure_TD - the amount of TD hours for the subject.
      heure_TP - the amount of TP hours for the subject.
      heure_CM - the amount of CM hours for the subject.
      heure_projet - the amount of project hours for the subject.
      Poid_CC - the weight of the exam.
      Type_CC - the type of exam.
      Poid_CT - the weigth of the final exam.
      Type_CT - the type of the final exam.
      poidMatiere - the weight of the subject in the UE.
